This paper discusses the security testing of industrial IoT applications, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the need for systematic and automated testing methods, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the threats to industrial systems, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
